Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,婚宴？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.28,0:03:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,而且是第9代
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.31,0:03:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.66,0:03:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们父母的婚宴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.75,0:03:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,来宾几乎都是普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.96,0:03:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是对一般社会大众举办的婚宴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.26,0:03:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,对夜樱家来说
